id":1282363,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa9e2eb83057a0406c4ef5ab69365135aa1a5ea","tid":1282363,"uid":53369,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"沙皇飯焦<br />\n老頂咪老懵董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"屌 今日佢仲話通識累事 原來係條傻鳩老懵董當年推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"董建華又承認，其任內推行的通識教育，是造成現時年輕人問題的主因之一，形容通識教育「直情失敗了」，要想辦法改。他續稱，香港人尤其年青人，應清楚了解國家，認為時下本地青年對國家發展不夠了解。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過當年力推通識成為必修科的官員，正是如今建制「大紅人」羅范椒芬和李國章。他們當年大力向各界推銷通識科，<span style=\"color: red;\">獲前特首董建華背書支持</span>。"},{"pid":"93ae5f5f6765346044b4d2368179d08e7e4ca7d7","tid":1282363,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fa9e2eb83057a0406c4ef5ab69365135aa1a5ea","tid":1282363,"uid":53369,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"沙皇飯焦<br />\n老頂咪老懵董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"小心貪曾打手一陣出嚟咬你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kp16Hv3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKp16Hv3.png&h=d6935eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n董建華啟動教改 羅范力推通識科<br />\n<br />\n被一些建制派人士欲除之而後快的通識科，其實是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">董建華在2001年施政報告</span></strong>中，表示政府打算在10年內落實高中三年制。當時社會關注一些中學生讀書只會死記硬背、高分低能，缺乏對社會和世界的認知，因此教育署課程發展議會於2001年10月初步敲定，會在新高中實行中、英、數必修之外，更增加必修通識科。時任主席黃玉山認為，通識科可培養學生的國際視野及人文質素。<br />\n<br />\n但有關建議，惹來教育界反彈，擔心通識科屬綜合學科，對教學資源和師資需求很大，若變成必修科會「難教難考」，最後只會將學生教至「通通都唔識」。況且，將通識納入必修科勢必引起教師「板塊大挪移」，其他選修科目教師可能飯碗不保，當然爭議極大。<br />\n<br />\n當時，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">曾先後任職教統局局長及常秘的羅范椒芬和前教統局局長李國章，是通識科的主要推手</span></strong>。羅范曾表示，希望培訓更多一專多能的通才，高中課程引入通識教育是要鼓勵學生思考，積極游說社會各界接納通識科。她亦頻頻約見中學校長、大學學者解釋政策，爭取他們配合。<br />\n<br />\n結果在他們的推動之下，政府於2004年推出教改諮詢，建議將通識列入必修科，並在翌年正式拍板。教師只須接受35至100小時的培訓，即可任教高中通識科。該科亦不會設基準試，以免增加教師壓力。2009年，新高中學制開始實施，第一批新制學生於2012年應考DSE文憑試，於通識科至少須考獲2級才能獲資助大學學位取錄。"},{"pid":"b3fbd19c64ed388ae253ed3d7007c690aaa9c62f","tid":1282363,"uid":80769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"只係老師好野<br />\n通識科本來就係國民教育啲fd黎<br />\n前排先話要取消今日香港呢個單元"},{"pid":"f4d3e230b522849fc4d4e2705177b7c7e6b21555","tid":1282363,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609d9503a9b9f280d61896e4b87a2dd16dcb9628","tid":1282363,"uid":53369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"387025e20910e580deaf090056298773e6c692de","tid":1282363,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa9e2eb83057a0406c4ef5ab69365135aa1a5ea","tid":1282363,"uid":53369,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"沙皇飯焦<br />\n老頂咪老懵董<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"屌 今日佢仲話通識累事 原來係條傻鳩老懵董當年推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"董建華又承認，其任內推行的通識教育，是造成現時年輕人問題的主因之一，形容通識教育「直情失敗了」，要想辦法改。他續稱，香港人尤其年青人，應清楚了解國家，認為時下本地青年對國家發展不夠了解。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過當年力推通識成為必修科的官員，正是如今建制「大紅人」羅范椒芬和李國章。他們當年大力向各界推銷通識科，<span style=\"color: red;\">獲前特首董建華背書支持</span>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"香港罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01fa4ba8215e273c43c2f8b8fd3c1231cb7c6c9","tid":1282363,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0b49d5c7b1beb0fc9ec003ce3037b19f48c7280","tid":1282363,"uid":53369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"751e496272fc07741f656df78e511ba0a6bc7ff3","tid":1282363,"uid":24160,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"93, 94後起嘅後生仔都受惠於此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"母語教學<br />\n男女合併派位<br />\n受惠你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"講梗通識科呀 <br />\n九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc0acabfb9df7ba06eb92ebffee5e6720c2ef83","tid":1282363,"uid":54902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"重點點必修必考個下先正"},{"pid":"eb18ed6dff300757699efe99e63678e1a9bd173f","tid":1282363,"uid":72945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"好多通識老師都係黃。反共反中"},{"pid":"827df1de040c5dfa64e1f0e28d1b71e6cef070d5","tid":1282363,"uid":149266,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b48e7eecd87ac94553e8b2bc44cbce30d71a58e9","tid":1282363,"uid":258681,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"其實已經有官話想鏟走通識科，就係因為我地識左批判性思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite